    .product-content
      h2 Historical Job Postings

      br

      .container-fluid
        .row
          .col-lg-9
            <b>Description</b>
            p This dataset consists of 4.2M job postings (7.7M job positions) published on Platsbanken from the year 2006 up to and including 2016. Texts have been anonymized with sentences including names, telephone numbers and email adresses removed. Each listing contains metadata on location, dates, employer name, job type and any additional job details.

            p For a visual overview of this dataset, please see the <a href="http://historik.azurewebsites.net/" target="_blank">dashboard example</a>.

            <b>API with basic statistics</b>
            p We provide a microservice for basic statistics and queries on the dataset. A notebook with examples can be found <a href="https://github.com/simonbe/afhistorik/blob/master/notebooks/API_description.ipynb" target="_blank">here</a> (under construction).

            <b>Examples</b>
            p <a href="http://historik.azurewebsites.net/" target="_blank">Dashboard</a> (<a href="https://github.com/simonbe/afhistorik" target="_blank">Source</a>) â€“ Visualize and explore the dataset. Uses the above API.

            <b>Data format</b>
            p Each line in a file contains a job listing in a JSON format (<a href="http://jsonlines.org/" target="_blank">JSON Lines</a>):

            pre
              | ...
              | {"ANTAL_AKT_PLATSER": "3", "PLATSBESKRIVNING": "...", ... }
              | {"ANTAL_AKT_PLATSER": "1", "PLATSBESKRIVNING": "...", ... }
              | {"ANTAL_AKT_PLATSER": "1", "PLATSBESKRIVNING": "...", ... }
              | ...

            p A listing has the following fields:

            .table-responsive
              table.table.table-bordered
                thead
                  tr
                    th Field
                    th Description
                tbody
                  tr
                    td ANTAL_AKT_PLATSER
                    td Number of placements
                  tr
                    td PLATSBESKRIVNING
                    td Job ad text
                  tr
                    td ADRESSLAND
                    td Country (Sweden if not specified)
                  tr
                    td AG_NAMN
                    td Employer name
                  tr
                    td ARBETSDRIFT
                    td Work information
                  tr
                    td ARBETSTID
                    td Working hours
                  tr
                    td BESKR_ARBETSDRIFT
                    td Additional work information
                  tr
                    td FORSTA_PUBLICERINGSDATUM
                    td Publication date
                  tr
                    td KOMMUN_KOD
                    td Municipality code
                  tr
                    td PLATSNUMMER
                    td Unique id
                  tr
                    td PLATSRUBRIK
                    td Job ad heading
                  tr
                    td POSTORT
                    td District
                  tr
                    td SISTA_ANSOK_PUBLDATUM
                    td Last apply date
                  tr
                    td TILLTRADE
                    td Admission information
                  tr
                    td VARAKTIGHET
                    td Duration
                  tr
                    td YRKE_ID
                    td Occupation id

            p All fields are strings and may be nullable, i.e. no data may be given for a field.

